      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
        Explore an innovative ecosystem designed for growth, efficiency, and seamless automation.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
